Vensun Pharmaceuticals, Inc. Key Developments

Vensun Pharmaceuticals, Inc. Appoints Joan Janulis as Senior Vice President of Regulatory Affairs and Compliance
Feb 12 16
Vensun Pharmaceuticals, Inc. announced the appointment of Joan Janulis as the Senior Vice President of Regulatory Affairs and Compliance. In this role Ms. Janulis will oversee the regulatory affairs, quality, and compliance functions. Ms. Janulis was most recently a Vice President and Head of the Regulatory Practice at Lachman Consultants.


