Vensun Pharmaceuticals, Inc., based in Yardley, Pennsylvania, was established in July 2011 and is an emerging pharmaceutical company developing a portfolio of generic prescription products in various dosage forms covering a broad range of therapeutic categories. The Company is co-developing the products with a number of strategic partners in the U.S. and overseas. The Company has four ANDAs approved, more than 15 filed ANDAs and has approximately 15 products in active development with various partners. Vensun also in-licensed over 25 products to expand and diversify its pipeline.






